{"tid":1814931,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"真正不捉鬼就係就算當眾爆玻璃個條友係黑警, 我地都要為佢拍手歡呼, 當佢係手足咁高度表揚","createTime":"2020-01-07T07:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T07:57:14.000Z","uid":66260,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4fa109c10163aed47cc97f8299f06332fff59af8","tid":1814931,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:02:57.000Z","msg":"要做到呢點, 先係真正嘅核爆唔割"},{"pid":"ffb28005f60a4547313b88c323be798c9f57230f","tid":1814931,"uid":101902,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:06:47.000Z","msg":"其實之前不嬲都係, e.g. 裝修黨鐵, 360, 大把人拍手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 係最近幾次先開始有捉鬼想死隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 睇直播見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb040b9d3e300b60028e33e7e5e75e1932831af9","tid":1814931,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:11:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c3fa3938382283f9ac83f338a4ff731780b4aa3","tid":1814931,"uid":273218,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:12:19.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係好耐<br />\n<br />\n否則唔會區選前中大poly打大仗周圍彈<br />\n<br />\n都大勝<br />\n<br />\n5毛連登分化放負燃，應該同黑警一樣死全家"},{"pid":"317843e327f607b67bfd600c80d47c9ded8896b1","tid":1814931,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:20:01.000Z","msg":"捉鬼作用=0, 大家咪再捉鬼"},{"pid":"98a6974561bc5302641775672881720b36113b0d","tid":1814931,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:22:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">既然曱甴頭話曱甴唔會做犯法野, 如果佢真係鬼, 又做犯法野, 係咪應該高聲歡呼<br />\n<br />\n如果佢唔係鬼, 當然要更大聲歡呼</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1dd33dfbb7ec26e1f935541294bf64d9cf6d7a93","tid":1814931,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98a6974561bc5302641775672881720b36113b0d","tid":1814931,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:22:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">既然曱甴頭話曱甴唔會做犯法野, 如果佢真係鬼, 又做犯法野, 係咪應該高聲歡呼<br />\n<br />\n如果佢唔係鬼, 當然要更大聲歡呼</span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:23:34.000Z","msg":"態度正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e0e38f1af7d69e6a72701e746d300d17875df9","tid":1814931,"uid":124636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"依個真"},{"pid":"27cd4082fc679c65657a18c6fb6d07c73ab9dbee","tid":1814931,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:25:33.000Z","msg":"鬼裝修割唔割？係咪對家計謀？且看割唔割席兩步曲，教你睇穿風向背後更深層嘅陰謀。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809005</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5b88f6d8b72ecc47de39e66f8d50b2dbe9bba3d6","tid":1814931,"uid":232817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:28:06.000Z","msg":"其實已經有唔少次係啲人講返，裝修現場其實大家都拍手支持，就算唔同意都係唔加入好少阻止（除非真係怕人命傷亡，eg太大火驚燒到上樓），但係睇返連登就會有一班人話現場啲人割，一班就會話自己勇武見到人割好傷心，所以其實對網上言論唔洗太認真"},{"pid":"94005254c8dc43c43bc6506261ad12ae3f29f88c","tid":1814931,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:29:14.000Z","msg":"正解<br />\n但好簡單 <br />\n鬼係真係鬼<br />\n捉鬼既 都係鬼<br />\n屌人捉鬼既 都有鬼<br />\n<br />\n當中當然有真心手足  但都要睇通劇本"},{"pid":"7adc4bc9cf066b06d2b074eda132120d81ead937","tid":1814931,"uid":279616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4fa109c10163aed47cc97f8299f06332fff59af8","tid":1814931,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:02:57.000Z","msg":"要做到呢點, 先係真正嘅核爆唔割"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:40:26.000Z","msg":"不能同意更多<br />\n<br />\n1. 根本就無方法可以100%捉啱鬼<br />\n2. 捉到又唔敢打撚死佢，鬼既數目唔會變少<br />\n3. 鬼做既野正正係大家想要既野，咁點解要捉、要阻？<br />\n4. 有無鬼搞搞震，班狗都會鳩拉鳩打，咁捉鬼黎有乜用？<br />\n<br />\n唯一希望可以一齊改善既，係唔需要將所有「功勞」都入鬼數。如果有人覺得：入錯鬼數=否定勇武功勞、唔入鬼數=畫面唔好睇會輸「民意」，咁不如大家一齊盡力歌頌呢類「功勞」，同時唔需要將個焦點放響「邊個」做。例：藍店被裝修、狗宿被燒，大家可以話：做得好！燒得好！而唔需要話：勇武做得好！或者：又係班鬼做！<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係做到！同埋全身而退！"},{"pid":"d81fa24660bc20c591b291a6827d9ce8410ac6e8","tid":1814931,"uid":211466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1dd33dfbb7ec26e1f935541294bf64d9cf6d7a93","tid":1814931,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98a6974561bc5302641775672881720b36113b0d","tid":1814931,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:22:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">既然曱甴頭話曱甴唔會做犯法野, 如果佢真係鬼, 又做犯法野, 係咪應該高聲歡呼<br />\n<br />\n如果佢唔係鬼, 當然要更大聲歡呼</span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:23:34.000Z","msg":"態度正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:52:25.000Z","msg":"自推<br />\n1"},{"pid":"4da228d08423974c23ff6c39ec12af8072cb622f","tid":1814931,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:52:59.000Z","msg":"其實點解會捉<br />\n有人裝修唔係好事黎咩"},{"pid":"9de3769db4c2a5e1e0e2337d8655c2fe8f3b9fa7","tid":1814931,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:53:23.000Z","msg":"唔理係咪鬼<br />\n爆支那野已經值得俾掌聲"},{"pid":"0550e598eeaae476d6651e592728dba417ce75d1","tid":1814931,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:54:06.000Z","msg":"請不要捉鬼！"},{"pid":"eb6b834c67ae215dd0ad043fd9247bf59392118b","tid":1814931,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:54:17.000Z","msg":"反對<br />\n100%係黑警<br />\n就割<br />\n<br />\n核爆唔割既對象係抗爭者<br />\n唔係狗"},{"pid":"9d68fa36b09f4c87471b44ed81bdaf73034f8547","tid":1814931,"uid":46282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca35d45d47e2288c1591c0ef7b005821565f39fa","tid":1814931,"uid":179703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fa109c10163aed47cc97f8299f06332fff59af8","tid":1814931,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:02:57.000Z","msg":"要做到呢點, 先係真正嘅核爆唔割"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:55:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b38bdbb078e6eb2ceb09d379ce2fb82d3f350434","tid":1814931,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3c03a87ca3b32787a8dd511ebffbd0f2fd6dbf","tid":1814931,"uid":269629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fa109c10163aed47cc97f8299f06332fff59af8","tid":1814931,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:02:57.000Z","msg":"要做到呢點, 先係真正嘅核爆唔割"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:57:14.000Z","msg":"其實咪等於popo射中自己友一樣<br />\n鬼係唔需要捉既<br />\n因為連popo都做唔到<br />\n如果popo落埋手 你當佢自己人咪得<br />\n<br />\n其實以住大遊行 指有不反個的<br />\n其他人做的咩 <br />\n行緊既人都唔會有咩特別反應 直行直過<br />\n保持同一態度<br />\n<br />\n如果有人煽動情緒<br />\n唔比反應就得<br />\n各有各做<br />\n半年來我地最學識就係依樣野"}]}